  "justification": "This post demonstrates excellent coherence with a clear narrative arc from rushed modern life to mindful sourdough baking, unified by the central metaphor of time. The writing flows smoothly with effective transitions between ideas. The informativeness is solid, offering genuine insights about sourdough's demands for patience and how this translates to broader life lessons, though it focuses more on personal reflection than technical details. Conciseness is the weakest aspect - while the prose is engaging, it includes some redundant phrasing and could convey the same insights more efficiently. Phrases like 'bubbly, demanding, and ultimately transformative' and extended metaphors, while stylistically pleasing, contribute to wordiness without proportional informational value."
}

